{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "第十五章「中计」\n\n唐花以精湛演技骗卫凤娘说赵无忌即将回来，卫凤娘深信不疑。唐花借口不希望让赵无忌看到自己而离开，卫凤娘感激落泪。事实上白玉雕龙计划正按唐傲设想推进。唐傲送下毒的千人参给上官怜怜，利用她的孝顺让她带给父亲上官刃服用。老祖宗与唐傲讨论计划风险后，提议杀白玉奇灭口。赵无忌回到赵公馆，卫凤娘把假日记交给他，赵无忌盛怒之下冲向上官堡。唐花奉命杀白玉奇，因白玉奇心脏偏右侥幸未死，取出抄写原本挣扎到赵公馆大门口。唐花生不安返回查看，发现尸体消失，循血迹到赵公馆门口找到尸体但未搜到原本，心中不安。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "你运气真好，据说赵无忌已经在回来这里的路途上，而且很可能明天就到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你是怎么知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "这还不简单，这里是大风堂的根据地之一，一定会有我们唐家堡的卧底的人，对不对？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我只要问问卧底在此的人，不就知道了？他们一定每天和唐家堡联络，像赵无忌这种大人物，怎么能不被唐家堡在各地的人追踪去向？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我唐花从未来过这里，这里的人也没见过我。而且他们只认识联络暗号，从不认人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "你不必谢我，我是心甘情愿替你做事的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我知道，赵无忌回来之后，我留在这里很不方便，所以..",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你要走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我不是说了吗？我留在这里很不方便。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我不要他的感激，我只要你..",
      "tone": "苦涩",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "那是不可能的，我的心里，只有无忌一个人，这是我早就跟你说过的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我不强求什么，我只要你心里偶而会想起我一下就足够了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我一定会时常想起你，你的大恩大德，我是绝对不会忘记的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "你只记得我的大恩大德吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "算了，反正我都准备离开了，一切都不再有什么意义了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你什么时候走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "现在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "现在？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "再待下去，我会疯掉。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "你保重。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "是什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "你打开看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "是千人参？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "是的，刚好有人从东北带来，我就买了。你身体太虚，需要补一补。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "这么贵重的东西，我怎么能吃？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "为什么不能？我这就去叫人来炖汤给你喝。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "不。",
      "tone": "拒绝",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "为什么？是我送给你的，我希望你早日复元呀！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我已经很好了，这两支人参，我留起来好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "可以吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "当然可以。已经是送给你的东西了，你爱怎么处理，就怎么处理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "你跟我之间还用得着谢谢这两个字吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "其实，你应该吃了这两支人参才对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "早点恢复体力，可以早点去你父亲身边。",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我已经好了。你看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "对呀，你再走几步看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你不是走得很好吗？你要不要明天就陪我找爹爹？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "你如果想的话，我当然奉陪。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "speaker_name": "上官怜怜",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_lian_lian",
      "text": "我会骗你吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我了解你心里的感受，我也知道你对赵无忌那种忿恨之情，但是，你要记住，现在是两个大帮派的大对决，千万不要因为一己之忿恨，而误了大事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "我不会的，老祖宗。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "万一怜怜去到上官堡，并不急着把人参给上官刃服用呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "我会用计来诱惑她，令她一定这样用。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你这么有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "当然，她的个性，我已经了若指掌了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "万一上官刃发现有异呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "怎么会？我们唐家的独门毒药，谁会察觉？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "万一他发现呢？我是说万一。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "万一他真的发现，我也不怕。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "因为我这次用的药，是最新的配方，是唐家第一次采用，我可以推托说那不是我们唐家的毒药。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "他会信吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "会的。第一，他没有理由怀疑我们会对他下毒，第二，我甚至可以把唐家的毒药谱拿给他看，他绝对找不到这份新配方和我们有什么关联的资料。而且，最重要的，我认为他根本不可能察觉。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你太自信了吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "这是你的遗传呀，老祖宗。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "好，我再来做一个假设，万一这药对上官刃不发生效用呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "那死的人是赵无忌，对我们根本没任何损失，除了让我会觉得有点遗憾之外。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你能这样想，可见你已经完全成熟，可以独当一面了。你不但已经能带领唐家，还可以带领消灭大风堂以后的霸业。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "老祖宗，我不会让你失望的。由这件事的各种可能性的发生，你相信我不会因私而忘公了吧？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我相信，我当然相信。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "唐花什么时候回来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "我叫他暂时留在赵公馆附近，监视卫凤娘的动静，等确定白玉雕龙的计划完成了再回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "这决定不错，不过，他应该还可以做一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "哦？做什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "把白玉斋的白玉奇杀了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你觉得白玉奇还有利用的价值吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "说不定以后还有用得着的地方。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我想不会了。你想想看，他被我们收买了十多年，到今天才用一次。而且这一次的事，也可以不必用到他的，你说对不对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "text": "我马上传书过去，要唐花立刻执行这件任务。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zu_zong",
      "speaker_name": "老祖宗",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "很好，这样你的白玉雕龙计划才会万无一失，知道吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "先别谈这个，你快跑过来，我给你看一样东西。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_zhao_wu_ji",
      "text": "你先去处理这件事吧，我在这里等你，一切等你回来再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "唐公子有事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "要我效劳的是——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "很简单的事，每个人都会的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "哦？唐公子的意思我不太懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "说得明白一点，我要你做的事只有三个字。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "三个字？写日记？又写日记？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "不。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "那是——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "赶快死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "赶快死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "我要你——赶快死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "死。死亡的死，你真听不懂？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "这么简单的道理你都不懂？当然是为了灭口。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "灭口？我替你们做了那么多年的事，我有泄露过什么吗？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "那为什么要灭口？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "因为任何事都会有第一次，任何事都是我们无法预料的。这叫预防胜于补救。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "白玉奇",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我——",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_bai_yu_qi",
      "text": "你不必再说了。我很喜欢你，但是我是奉命行事而已。你要自己了断，还是——",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    }
  ],
